  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2><img src="/media/13052601/levi-hotel-spa-levitunturi-childrens-playhouse.jpg" alt="ChildcareOptions" data-udi="umb://media/af8cbe767a14477c808bf56e99b723a0" /></h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Austria</h2>
<h3>Obergurgl</h3>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/0e86ba998418476eb4fbc95f5a146c0b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0e86ba998418476eb4fbc95f5a146c0b}" title="Hotel Bellevue">Hotel Bellevue</a></h4>
<p><strong>Ages - 2+</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Free Child Supervision in the children’s area (from 2 years)</li>
<li>Lunch for Children can be arranged locally (local charge)</li>
<li>Early evening meals for children are possible, one parent needs to be present, afterwards children can be dropped off at children’s club, Games Room, Playroom</li>
</ul>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/6e448fc9d4404ad59b2952657506e71d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6e448fc9d4404ad59b2952657506e71d}" title="Hotel Edelweiss &amp; Gurgl">Hotel Edelweiss &amp; Gurgl</a></h4>
<p><strong>Ages - 4+</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Kids Club</li>
<li>Child Supervision (from 4 years), free on certain days/hours</li>
<li>Games room</li>
<li>Children's menu, early meals for children available</li>
<li>Baby listening service</li>
</ul>
<h3>Saalbach</h3>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/29de78776d5a4a89a06c90fe08478019" href="/{localLink:umb://document/29de78776d5a4a89a06c90fe08478019}" title="Hotel Sonne">Hotel Sonne</a></h4>
<p><strong>Ages - 2+</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Child Supervision for 2-10year olds five days per week</li>
<li>Babysitting available on request</li>
</ul>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/6fd6e0b17cba446e877b4abb5a390fbb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6fd6e0b17cba446e877b4abb5a390fbb}" title="Gardenhotel Theresia">Gardenhotel Theresia</a></h4>
<p><strong>Ages - 3+</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Kids Club runs Monday – Friday (lunch, drink and afternoon snack included) (ages 3 and up)</li>
<li>Play Area</li>
<li>Teenager’s Lounge with indoor table tennis table, ping pong table, Nintendo switch, table football and air hockey</li>
<li>Children’s menu or children’s buffet</li>
<li>Early meals available (Highchairs) in restaurants</li>
</ul>
<h3>Seefeld</h3>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/6c2a0c7ef6234927bf68265e9fed9f69" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6c2a0c7ef6234927bf68265e9fed9f69}" title="Alpenpark Resort">Alpenpark Resort</a></h4>
<p><strong>Ages - Check directly</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Early child meals available from 18:00pm</li>
<li>Free baby buggies, bouncers, cots and other baby equipment</li>
<li>Children’s fun world with waterslides, paddling pools and adventure area</li>
</ul>
<h3>Hinterglemm</h3>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/12cb1dd201c0496f9a3650d30816a0fa" href="/{localLink:umb://document/12cb1dd201c0496f9a3650d30816a0fa}" title="Hotel Alpine Palace">Hotel Alpine-Palace </a></h4>
<p><strong>Ages - 3+</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Children’s Supervision from 3 years old: Sun- Fri (lunch paid locally)</li>
<li>Games room</li>
<li>Children’s menu and early meals available</li>
</ul>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">France</h2>
<h3>Les Arcs</h3>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/594cf30ffc6d4109a4fcf70f16b4aa1a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/594cf30ffc6d4109a4fcf70f16b4aa1a}" title="Hotel Les Mélèzes (Arc 2000)">Hotel Les Melezes</a></h4>
<p><strong>Ages - 4+</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Free Kids and juniors club for children 4-10years old from Monday to Friday, for half a day</li>
<li>Free teen club for 11-17years from Monday to Friday (during French school holidays)</li>
<li>Baby club for children aged 18months – 3years (pre book). Monday – Friday / 5 half days (Change made during French school holidays)</li>
<li>Children’s menu including early meals (highchairs available) in restaurant</li>
<li>Indoor play area with -  Books, DVDs, board games, puzzles and music available for children</li>
</ul>
<h3>Tignes</h3>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/c9cd744ad4364e86a0ce2a71fc25c3c3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c9cd744ad4364e86a0ce2a71fc25c3c3}" title="Hotel Val Claret All Inclusive">Val Claret All inclusive </a></h4>
<p><strong>Ages - 3+</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Children’s Club 3-5years is open all season, 6-10years open during French school holidays, 11-17 open during French school holidays</li>
<li>Supervised support for 3-10years old to ski lessons</li>
</ul>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/c458d67f05c14477ae868054e26e9c23" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c458d67f05c14477ae868054e26e9c23}" title="Village Montana Hotel">Village Montana Hotel</a></h4>
<p><strong>Ages - 3+</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Children’s playroom</li>
<li>Free hotel kids club for children 3-10years old, during French school holidays – Sunday – Friday (pre-book)</li>
<li>Babysitting services are available (book and pay locally)</li>
<li>Earlier meal times for children are available (on request and in French school holidays only)</li>
</ul>
<h3>Avoriaz</h3>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/7a167125394045d79758340e629fb7bf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7a167125394045d79758340e629fb7bf}" title="Hotel Les Cimes du Soleil">Hotel Les Cimes du Soleil</a></h4>
<p><strong>Ages - 3+</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Kids clubs are all included : 3-5years is available all season and are 6 continuous days, 6-10 years are during French school holidays, 11-17 open during French school holidays</li>
<li>Kids Clubs may include themed activities, indoor activities, arts, crafts, dancing, singing, stories, creative workshops and end of week performance</li>
<li>Register on arrival, activity leaders are qualified and speak English<br /><br /></li>
</ul>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Italy</h2>
<h3>Ortisei</h3>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/155b1fe76a3d46e3b177207561dda831" href="/{localLink:umb://document/155b1fe76a3d46e3b177207561dda831}" title="Adler Spa Resort Dolomiti">Adler Spa Resort</a></h4>
<p><strong>Ages - 4+</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>AKI kids club for children aged4+ (supervised, available on request)</li>
<li>Playroom, Children’s Cinema, Video game corner</li>
<li>Children’s spa Treatments</li>
<li>A cot is available for 20 Euros a day (based on 2023 pricing - this is subject to change)</li>
<li>Highchairs in restaurant</li>
</ul>
<h3>Cervinia</h3>
<h4><a data-udi="umb://document/1bcb2850b410443ebf005bd5fc20e5e6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1bcb2850b410443ebf005bd5fc20e5e6}" title="Valtur Cervinia Cristallo Ski Resort">Hotel Valtur</a></h4>
<p><strong>Ages - 3+</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Games rooms</li>
<li>Kid’s play area</li>
<li>Free childcare daily for 3 to 13years</li>
<li>It is possible to book lunch childcare locally at an additional cost</li>
</ul>
<p><em>Please note - Childcare is bookable directly with your selected hotel, not with Inghams, therefore guests will need to arrange any of the above childcare options directly with the property. Inghams cannot book this on your behalf. Inghams cannot guarantee availability. </em></p>
<h2><img src="/media/13070618/inghams-best-family-ski-resorts-arinsal.jpg" alt="FamilyFriendlySkiResorts" data-udi="umb://media/c25d1cf916bf41a389d3ca6d240b02f7" /></h2>
<h2>Family friendly ski resorts:</h2>
<p>Here are a few more resorts that offer some great family friendly attributes.</p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Austria</h2>
<p><strong>Obertauern</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Reliable conditions, snow-sure resort</li>
<li>Circular resort so you can start and end your day in the same spot</li>
<li>Family friendly accommodation close to the slopes</li>
</ul>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Andorra</h2>
<p><strong>Arinsal</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Good value accommodation</li>
<li>Free lift pass for children under 12 when parents pre-book passes</li>
<li>Free helmet hire for children when equipment is prebooked</li>
<li>Gentle runs, great for confidence building</li>
<li>English speaking ski school</li>
</ul>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Switzerland</h2>
<p><strong>Wengen</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Offers slopes for all ability levels, as well as a range of off slope activities</li>
<li>Part of the wider Jungfrau ski area</li>
<li>Benefits from a traffic free system</li>
<li>Free lift pass for children up to 5 years old</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Saas Fee</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Traffic free resort</li>
<li>Family friendly atmosphere</li>
<li>Larger beginners area in resort with good progression opportunities</li>
<li>Lots to do off the slopes</li>
<li>Free children's helmet when booking skis and boots</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Davos</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Free child's lift pass up to 5yrs</li>
<li>Free child skis and boots when 2 adults pre-book</li>
<li>We work with some great local ski schools</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Zermatt</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Free child's helmet when booking skis and boots</li>
<li>Free child's skis and boots when 2 adults pre book</li>
<li>Free child's lift pass</li>
<li>Learning Zones for beginners, plus a childrens snowpark with magic carpets – good progression as well.</li>
<li>Plenty of skiing for the whole family</li>
<li>Great choice of accommodation</li>
<li>High altitude</li>
<li>Car free</li>
</ul>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">France</h2>
<p><strong>Avoriaz</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Good for beginner and intermediates, extensive ski area</li>
<li>Many ski in, ski out accommodation options</li>
<li>ESF ski school is great for beginners/ improvers</li>
<li>Lots to do off the slopes</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Flaine</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Free lift pass for all children under 8 years old</li>
<li>Ski in, ski out accommodation</li>
<li>Range of beginner slopes plus free magic carpets – progression opportunities are good as there is greens and blues in the bowl.</li>
<li>Family friendly resort with plenty to do off of the slopes</li>
</ul>]]></bodyText>
